modName: Dragonplate should be better than Daedric
summary: DSBBTD simply swaps the Value and Armor Rating of Daedric and Dragonplate armors so that Dragonplate is better than Daedric.
descriptionHtml:
I didn\'t see anything around that just got this done so I took the time to do it myself.

For players who would prefer it this way, DSBBTD simply swaps the Value and Armor Rating of Daedric and Dragonplate armors so that Dragonplate is better than Daedric.

 ~ LtMattmoo
